2. Tap the ndax logo at the top left to open the menu.&lt;br&gt;
3. Select &quot;Trade&quot; from the menu.&lt;br&gt;
4. Tap the orders icon in the bottom right corner of the screen.&lt;br&gt;
5. Locate the open order you want to cancel.&lt;br&gt;
